data.description: Light, bright townhome in beautiful, quiet Mesquite community now available! This home is a dream with plenty of natural light, high ceilings, open floor plan and ample sized bedrooms. The living space is perfect for entertaining or for a quiet evening at home. The master bedroom boasts an oversized walk-in closet, en suite bathroom with his and hers sinks. Enjoy the covered patio with expansive golf course and mountain views.
